    "rtlPodcastExcludes": "DeezerAudiobook,MusicAlbum,MusicArtist,MusicPlaylist,MusicRadio,MusicSong,MusicTrack,PodcastEpisode,PodcastFormat,PrhAudiobook,WatchMovie,WatchTvSeries,WatchTvShow"
